Jump Welcome to use "foreign teacher supermarket".Foreign teachers supermarket is a comprehensive foreign language learning platform, including live classes, online classes, private teaching courses, nearby institutions discount courses.In order to provide the above services, the following permissions of your device shall be invoked during the use of this application: networking, storage, phone, location, address book, camera, microphone, and album permissions, and the following information of you shall be collected and used: 
 ● Networking: In order to better use the app, all display information should be displayed in the connected state
 ● Storage: Used to save pictures and videos 
 ● Telephone: Used for calling customer service phone 
 ● Location: used to post status, you can find nearby friends, view nearby teaching and training institutions discount course information 
 ● Camera: Camera permissions will be applied for for better interaction in live classes
 ● Microphone: To interact with live lecturers in order to live class
 ● Album: You can set avatars and publish status 
 ● Address book: In order to help you find more friends, we may apply for address book access.
 ● We respect your choice. If you do not wish to be recommended to others, you can turn it off at any time in the "Me-Settings-Privacy Settings" section.
 ● Address book, precise geolocation, camera, microphone, photo album permissions are not enabled by default and are only used with your express authorization for specific functions or services. You may also revoke the authorization.In particular, even if you authorize us to obtain these sensitive permissions, we will not collect your information when the relevant functions or services are not needed. 
 If you do not agree with the above information we collect, or do not agree to call the relevant mobile permissions, the application will not work properly. The messaging push function provided by this application is supported by a third party.In order to realize real\-time message push, intelligent push based on user portrait and situational push based on offline location information, the following information of you shall be collected and used during the application: 
 ● User ID creation: In order to create the user ID required for push service, we may need to collect the following device information: such as IMEI, Android ID, device serial number, MAC, Android Advertisement ID, IMSI, etc.This information will be used to generate a unique push target ID, known as CID.
 ● Improve push ability: In order to provide better push service and experience, such as push ability using the manufacturer's system, we may need to collect the following device information: device manufacturer, device brand, device model, Android version, Rom information.
 ● Intelligent push function: In order to implement refined push operation based on user portrait and recommend push content more in line with your needs, we may need to collect the following application information: APP installation list, APP Active list information.
 ● Situational push function: In order to realize the ability to push messages based on users' offline scenes and recommend push content more suitable for your needs, we may need to collect the following user information: network information (including IP address, MAC information, WIFI list, base station information), and location related information (longitude and latitude).
 
 If you do not agree with the above information collected by us, or do not agree to call the relevant mobile permissions, some functions will not be able to be used normally.
